Kono, holi no ɓe kaɓirtee ? Mbele ko duko, mbele ko ƴattooje, mbele ko tooñde walla nii añde leƴƴi goɗɗi ? Mbiy-ɗen ko alaa e ɗii laabi fof potngol huutoreede

Annduɓe ene mbiya “jiɗɗo naneede e manteede, yo anndinir yimɓe hoyre mum ko moƴƴi, gila e haala haa e golle”
 Waɗde so en njiɗii ngol men tinee, nanee, mantee, cinkiren ngol feeñninde ko ngol anndiraa koo
 Ɗuum woni nehdi, hulde gacce, hormaade neɗɗo fof, daraade e goonga
 Laataade leñol ngol tooñataa, heertotaako, jiɗngol leƴƴi fof, ganndiraangol teddungal e waawde moƴƴinde gondigal
 Sabu men faamde e yenaneede, yiɗde leñol mum, firtaani añde leƴƴi goɗɗi
 Mi haalaani ko foti wonde ñaawoore biyɗo yimɓe leñol goɗngol biyaate bonɗe, nde mbiyaani mbaɗaani, kono ene hulɓinii, ɗo cikketenooɗo ko “ngenndiyanke” darotoo ene manta kaaloowo e mo tooñaani ɗum haalaluuji ɗi peewaani, njuɓɓaani, ɗi aada salii, tee kawraani e diine
