Goomuuji losko parlamaaji peeñii ko adii tippule demokaraasiije, kono ɗi ɓeydiima semmbe e huuñɗeede no feewi he sahaa nde yiɗaa tabitingol kam e pooɗanaagol laamuuji potal, laamuuji goonga
