 Ɓe ngoni ɗoon kadi duuɓi tati, ɓe mbaɗi kawgel goɗngel e hitaande 1934 ngam ɓennude e duɗal goɗngal ɓurngal ngaal toowde
 Alla hoddiraani o waɗa ngeel kawgel sabu woon tonngi
 O waɗtoyi kawgel  goɗngel paytungel e karallaagal ndema, e hitaande ndee wootere, o ari hoore
 Nii woni, o faynaa Luga
