1- Jokkondire
Caggal nde ɓe ndiisnii haralleeɓe jaŋde mawɓe, ɓe keɓi humpito e caɗeele duɗe cosanooɗe e nder leegal ngal, ɓe njoñi daarti waañooɓe nayeeɓe, haa alaa ko hedditii hankadi so wonaa golle, ɓe njokkondiri e rajo ngam waɗde eeraango
 Ɓe njaɓɓi koyɗe maɓɓe, kamɓe sukaaɓe ɓee haa to Ceerno Haamiidu Baal, almaami raatib leegal ngal, ɓe kabri ɗum miijo maɓɓe
 Ɓe nduttii kadi ɓe neli toon jinnaaɗo maɓɓe debbo mbele ena ɓeydoo semmbinde koyɗe maɓɓe gadane ɗee
 Ɓe ɓenni to hooreejo njuɓɓudi leegal hono Aamadu Konnaate, ɓe kaalani ɗum eɓɓoore nde ɓe njogii
