 Ko njiy-mi e ccaaɗngol biyeteengol Gorgol danewol, tuggude ɗo yuppata e maati, fa’ti fuɗnaange, nano e ñaamo maggol fof hikka toɓaaka
 Seeɗa toɓnooɗo heen oo haarnataano jawdi saka waɗa ñoomre
 To gese jeeri jabbaaka, waalo ne ilaano saka jabbee
 Ko faayre mawnde ! Ko ɗum saabii gila e lewru noowammbar 2014 jawdi ndii fuɗɗii uujde fa’de worgo

