Yeru goɗɗo bonannde jawdi, ko kanndaa keso oo
 Ina wiyee wonde e hitaande 2009, nde Muhammed Abdel Asiis, persidaa Muritani yahi to Turki, yiyndiri e hooreejo ndiin leydi, hono Erdogan, ɓe kaaldiino haala kanndaa moƴƴo wonannde Muritani
 Oon halfini kabine mahngo kanndaaji leydi mum ina wiyee TAV, mo nganndu-ɗaa ko kam hesɗitini kanndaa Istammbul e mo Tunus e yoga e kanndaaji Orop fuɗnaange, e mo Doha, yo yuurnitano Muritani ko waawi waɗeede
 TAV ina seedtanaa no feewi mbaawka to oon bannge
