 Nde tawnoo ko jamma Mawluud hawri, hiirde ndee udditiraa ko Al-Quraan, caggal ɗuum ko jimɗi Nulaaɗo Alla Muhammadu (JKM) e daaɗe naalankooɓe diiwaan oo
