 Ko ɗuum nii woni ko Jallo Mammadu Bacca, kalifu ndeenka leydi, mo o nulnoo to asaambele e to senaa ngam faamninde fiilaaɓe ɓee nafoore wonnde e jaɓgol eɓɓaande mbayliigu nguu

