 Mo wiyi sodorde noon, wiyi ustagol fere (ɗoo maa ɗe usto fotde feccere (50%)), ɗum noon ngañaari wonande njulaaagu hakkunde leyɗe ɗiɗi ɗee e yimɓe ɓee

