Ɗoyru ko ñawu mbonngu, ndaaɓoowu, mbaroowu so tawii gonduɗo heen yaawaani safraade, maa walla so rewaani safaara mum no fotiri
 Ñawu nguu heɓrotoo ko e weeyo
