 Ɗuum ko caggal nde ñaawirdu Pretoriyaa weddii haɗoore mo yaltude leydi Afirik bannge worgo, tuma nde o arnoo nootitaade batu kuuɓtodinngu 25ɓu fedde Ngootaagu Afrik (UA), jooɗinoongu tuggude 7 haa 15 lewru suwee 2015 to Johanesburg
