 Nde Koreera ruttanii jaabtaade naamnde berlanooɗe, laaɓtinii yoga e toɓɓe, remtii won e purge, ɗe jale mum arano duuɗnoo
 Nde o rowi, Ceerno Abdul Sidiiki Kebe uddiri yeewtere ndee duwaawu
