Faandaare nanondiral ngal ko waɗde feere mbele pine fof ina teskee e tabitingol politikaaji pine, ngam fotndude yimɓe fof, fotnda fartaŋŋeeji mum en waawde naftoraade pine nokkuyankooje e pine goɗɗe winndere ndee

