Mboɗo haawaa wiyooɓe kaalataa ɗemɗe goɗɗe, kono so njiyii jeyaaɗo e leñol goɗngol ene haala Pulaar tan mbeltoo
 Jiɗɗo ma kay, yiɗ ɗum
 Kaalɗo ɗemngal maa kay, woto salo haalde ngal mum
