 Ñalnde 21 desaambar 2018 kadi, laamuuji leyɗe ɗiɗi ɗee ciifdiino nanondire cakkitiiɗe ngam gollodaade e yeñtinidde gaas jiytaaɗo nder geec e keerol hakkunde leyɗe ɗiɗi ɗee

