 Tiitoonde mayre ko “caɗeele renndo men hannde” 

Jeewtuɗo oo ko Nasiiru Hammee Sih mo Haayre Mbaara e Sumeraaji
 Ndee yeewtere ko faayodinnde sabu alaa biyoowo mbiy-mi mo anndaa caɗeele men hannde
