 Ɗaam enɗam mboɗo nanngi ɗum haa tiiɗi
 Tee, e maɓɓe mo njiɗ-mi yiyde fof, mi yiyat ɗum, kadi kala e maɓɓe nodduɗo mi, mi noototo
 Kono e dingiral politik ngal, gooto e amen fof won ko goongɗini
