 Sabu emin piɓi laamu keɓtaangu e juuɗe amen nguu, ene foti artude ɗo wonnoo

Naamnal : Mate a waawaa wallude Makki haa laamtoo, daroo wallu maa haa lomto-ɗaa ɗum so joofnii daawe mum ɗiɗi ɗee ?
