 Ngoon ɗoon jarribo fotnoo waɗde ko e daawal duuɓi jeegom tawa, e nder jaŋde les-lesre nde, ina farlinaa e sukaaɓe safalɓe janngude ɗemngal arab ; sukaaɓe ɓaleeɓe ɓee noon mbellitaa suɓaade hakkunde ɗemngal Arab e ɗemngal Farayse (Arab e Farayse)
