 Ko ɗoon ɓe tawi ko ɓuri heewde e jibinannde Sorimalee gila e joom-wuro ngoo, nulaaɓe batu Sorimalee ummoriiɓe to Nuwaasaot haa e yontannde rewɓe e worɓe
 Ko ɓeen calmini ɓe, mbismii ɓe
 Tawi ko adii ɗuum, sukaaɓe wuro ngoo coppii coɓoƴƴi, pertiima cate leɗɗe, pittii nokku ɗo daakaa oo ɗoo haa laaɓi, mbeertii heen leece haa o hawri
 To bannge ndiyam, ko saretaaji ngaddoyi barile, sukaaɓe rewɓe kocci ƴoogirɗe mbaɗi ɗe haa ɗe keewi
